hackathon-rules:
There will be adult supervision at the event at all times. At night at 7pm, doors will close and lock until 7am the next morning. We will be following the MLH code of conduct (
) and Hacker Fund Parent Packet.
You will need a valid student ID (or some sort of ID), chargers, your phone, a blanket/sleeping bag, toiletries, a signed parent packet (either paper copy or email confirmation), and any supplies you need for your hack. Some hardware will be available for rent at the event. High quality mac desktops are provided for every attendee, but feel free to bring your own laptop.
